de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.persistence

Class DatabaseTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.persistence.DatabaseTest

  • public class DatabaseTest
extends Object
    Test cases for mapping between database and POJO classes. Testing of database queries. This test backups the old database (directory copy) and is working on an empty one. After tests, the backup database is restored. It is recommended to run this test with an empty database.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
